      <title>汽车零部件制造商 Standard Profil 聘请顾问进行债务再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/car-parts-maker-standard-profil-hires-adviser-to-refinance-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汽车零部件供应商 Standard Profil Automotive GmbH 聘请了顾问，准备在更广泛的汽车行业危机中为其债务进行再融资。]]></description>
